summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Northwest Leschi and South Leschi Action Area urban renewal projects (NDP No. Wash. A-2); authorizing acquisition of property in Block 2, Hick's Addition to the City of Seattle, Blocks 6, 7 and 8, Baxter's Addition to the City of Seattle, Block 6, Ayer & O'Hara's Addition to the City of Seattle, Block 12, Thirtieth Avenue Addition to the City of Seattle, and Blocks 3 and 4, White's Addition to Seattle.
